column2: select a.eid, Age_at_recruitment_#, Sex_#, Ethnic_background_#, Age_started_wearing_glasses_or_contact_lenses_#, Qualifications_#, Reason_for_glasses_contact_lenses_#, Height_#, Weight_#, Body_mass_index_BMI__#, Intra_ocular_pressure_Goldmann_correlated_right__#, Intra_ocular_pressure_Goldmann_correlated_left__#, Intra_ocular_pressure_corneal_compensated_right__#, Intra_ocular_pressure_corneal_compensated_left__# from dbo.Baseline_characteristics b inner join dbo.Intraocular_pressure a cross apply openjson (Intra_ocular_pressure_Goldmann_correlated_right__#) j cross apply openjson (Intra_ocular_pressure_Goldmann_correlated_left__#) h cross apply openjson (Intra_ocular_pressure_corneal_compensated_right__#) i cross apply openjson (Intra_ocular_pressure_corneal_compensated_left__#) k on a.eid = b.eid inner join dbo.Ethnicity e on a.eid = e.eid inner join dbo.Eyesight y on a.eid = y.eid inner join dbo.Body_size_measures o on a.eid = o.eid inner join dbo.Education d on a.eid = d.eid where j.value IS NOT # OR h.value IS NOT # OR i.value IS NOT # OR k.value IS NOT #
